                <note rend="inline" type="source">890F.515/16: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Appointed Minister Resident in Saudi Arabia</hi>
                        (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Moose</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Jidda</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-06-24T16:00:00+03:06"
                            >June 24, 1943—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 8:34 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>58. My 55, June 22, 5 p.m. Today a sovereign costing $21 will purchase only 38½
                    riyals making riyal value 54.54 cents. No new gold has yet arrived.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moose</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
